casebody.data:
March 23, 1959. No. 467, No. 541,

Misc.

Misc.

Stewart v. Green, Superintendent, Marion Correctional Institution, et al.; and Costello v. Klinger, Superintendent, California Men's Colony.

Motions for leave to file petitions for writs of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers "submitted as petitions for writs of certiorari, certiorari is denied.
